{"type": "article", "id": 21428, "title": "那些狗窝设计，总是带有一厢情愿的色彩", "description": "狗窝设计这件事儿吧，狗狗们通常没啥发言权。就怕设计师们一厢情愿地认为它们会喜欢。", "date": "2016-01-28T14:52:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 22834, "name": "狗窝"}, {"id": 752, "name": "宠物"}, {"id": 811, "name": "家居"}, {"id": 9484, "name": "猫奴"}, {"id": 22835, "name": "狗狗"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 114, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152902oTUAZvjcdxt36p8Q.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t去年夏天，《设计：为了爱犬》展览在上海喜玛拉雅美术馆举办，这是日本平面设计师原研哉策划的一个展览，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/13840.html\" target=\"_blank\">我们曾详细地报道过它</a>。那时原研哉提出了“狗的建筑”这一概念，他认为在为宠物设计窝时，设计师们应与宠物充分互动和相处，这样才能避免人一厢情愿、“不知狗之乐”的情况。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t今天我们将再介绍几款有设计感的狗窝，比如泰国设计事务所 <a href=\"http://www.deesawat.com/\">DEESAWAT</a> 设计的这款。<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/01/27/this-outdoor-sofa-is-designed-for-people-and-pets/\" target=\"_blank\">这是一款人与宠物同坐的沙发</a>，宠物有它们的专属空间，沙发坐垫可调节，你可以和爱猫/爱犬在同一个沙发上和平相处了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021528544TfD2Q185RrxILhP.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"460\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t沙发的名字叫 PET，设计师说室内室外皆可使用\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152855no2rC1qlzUP7vILB.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t你可以在附带的小桌上看书，狗狗则有它的专属空间\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152856LRB1wa0S3CGijTYH.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152856cfEQuw7ltpOSz0b3.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152857rXq1VhzJ3vTgZwW6.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"265\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t下面这几款狗窝则来自韩国品牌 <span><a href=\"http://www.badmarlon.com/\">Bad Marlon</a></span>，这个工作室的专长是<a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3055920/wanted/the-most-beautiful-dog-houses-come-from-this-south-korean-company#8\" target=\"_blank\">为小型犬设计窝</a>。这些窝大多便于清洗和拆卸，有着简洁的几何造型。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152857rmUCEIW2s0OP4gBn.jpg\" width=\"747\" height=\"500\" title=\"简洁的几何造型\" alt=\"简洁的几何造型\" data-ratio=\"0.66934404\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>简洁的几何造型</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152858y23UQZ9Md1cmDVEa.jpg\" width=\"404\" height=\"500\" title=\"这款则易于清洗\" alt=\"这款则易于清洗\" data-ratio=\"1.23762376\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这款则易于刷洗</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152858exHLK9PRj6CyXa1T.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"464\" title=\"“白富美”的小窝\" alt=\"“白富美”的小窝\" data-ratio=\"0.61866667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">白色小城堡\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152859kiubrYlq3gXZ7KCI.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\"“豪宅”\" alt=\"“豪宅”\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152859ZnSbUOv5gTfHJxpL.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152900AC2ashl6tWTfGbH3.jpg\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.75075075\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152901kHe8RI4Y1Zw5WdTi.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215290115Uh8Hc6dMmPaXRj.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"449\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.59866667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152902XzqDruoL8STA0JgN.jpg\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.75075075\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这款窝的亮点和缺陷都在于镂空的设计。镂空可令光线穿过，主人能在窝外观察宠物活动，但这也增大了清洗难度。如果你想查看更多与狗狗有关的设计，可以点击<a href=\"http://dog-milk.com\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/01/27/this-outdoor-sofa-is-designed-for-people-and-pets/\" target=\"_blank\">contemporist</a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}